videos.headline: Mixon hurdles defender for TD
videos.description: Joe Mixon jumps over a Kansas State defender for the 8-yard touchdown, increasing the Sooners' lead to 14-0.

videos.headline: Ertz's 2-yard TD run puts Wildcats back in game
videos.description: Jesse Ertz run for 2-ysrds for a TD

videos.headline: Mixon-Westbrook passing game is on point
videos.description: Oklahoma RB Joe Mixon takes the handoff, retreats to remain behind the line of scrimmage and finds Dede Westbrook for a 26 yard-TD, increasing the Sooners' lead to 21-7.

videos.headline: Kansas State QB pulls himself from game
videos.description: Kansas State QB Jesse Ertz asks for injury substitution after throwing poor pass

videos.headline: Kansas State interception stops Mayfield in his tracks
videos.description: Baker Mayfield's pass is intercepted by Kansas State DB Dante Barnett and picked off by DB Duke Shelley at the Kansas State 15.

videos.headline: Westbrook open for the Oklahoma 8-yard TD
videos.description: Baker Mayfield pass complete to Dede Westbrook for 8-yards for a TD

videos.headline: Hubener, Heath connect for 54-yard TD
videos.description: Kansas State QB Joe Hubener buys enough time to find an open WR Dominique Heath for a 54-yard touchdown, cutting the Sooners' lead to 31-17.

videos.headline: Westbrook takes flight for 88-yard TD
videos.description: For the second time today, Baker Mayfield makes a long pass to Dede Westbrook, who takes off to the end zone for the 88-yard touchdown to put Oklahoma up 38-17.
